    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249070/extras/8348ab66d16261ebafa30f598a2b014c.poster.avif?t=1725108199\" width=616 height=458 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249070/extras/8348ab66d16261ebafa30f598a2b014c.webm?t=1725108199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249070/extras/8348ab66d16261ebafa30f598a2b014c.mp4?t=1725108199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >概要</h2>90年代风格格斗游戏Strip Fighter系列作的原点，充满着色气和各种致敬要素登场了！<br><br><br>聚集了一群危险格斗家们的黑暗武斗大会。<br>现在，这场战斗即将开幕！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >角色</h2>冻杀拳的使用者 <strong>小雪</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249070/extras/79c920db10ced5bd10e90fa25382b6aa.avif?t=1725108199\" width=150 height=150 /></span><br>为了使自己拳法登峰造极而不停修练的年轻女格斗家<br><br>狂野大小姐 <strong>真麻</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249070/extras/1ec40097cb4bbb215ffeaba7c9a31c2b.avif?t=1725108199\" width=150 height=150 /></span><br>为了追求刺激而投身于战场的大小姐<br><br>摔角练习生 <strong>天田</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249070/extras/211bb903a8d091da12c0cea614ea151f.avif?t=1725108199\" width=150 height=150 /></span><br>为了展示摔角技巧的强大而奋斗的摔角练习生<br><br>迷路的孩子 <strong>蜜柑</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249070/extras/35cc7d17940ed2e3d5472d36c81ad940.avif?t=1725108199\" width=150 height=150 /></span><br>寻找失踪主人的少女<br><br>孤高女格斗家 <strong>雪莉</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249070/extras/b06f84fb5d0a762ab68edadbfa896e6a.avif?t=1725108199\" width=150 height=150 /></span><br>为了寻求强敌，因此参加战斗的女格斗家<br><br>水流拳继承者 <strong>水丽</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249070/extras/3ff976968ea7cabbbc2d40fd7542d7c0.avif?t=1725108199\" width=150 height=150 /></span><br>为了证明自家流派的强大而参加格斗大会的古武术继承者<br><br>暗格斗家 <strong>Ｓ</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249070/extras/af1dfdda52dfebc9556baed0169774d8.avif?t=1725108199\" width=150 height=150 /></span><br>沉浸于暴力让对手屈服的危险男人<br><br>淫魔 <strong>魅魔</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249070/extras/fa36a5d510b460d7600200034ae48483.avif?t=1725108199\" width=150 height=150 /></span><br>策划着以格斗大会为饵食吸收强者们淫力的淫魔<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >系统</h2><strong>STRIP连击</strong><br>使用STRIP计量表即可发动的强力必杀技。<br>按下↓→↓→+攻击可发动。<br>根据强弱不同有等级1～3，越强力的技能会消费越多计量表。<br>可发动弱攻击等级1、中攻击等级2、强攻击等级3的STRIP连击。<br><br><strong>STRIP Rush</strong><br>RUSH计量表在1以上时，按下X+A+B(R)发动。<br>在一定时间内的攻击都可取消。<br>RUSH计量表在被攻击时，与时间经过可回复，每回合结束都会重置。<br>计量表越多时发动时的时间暂停与效果持续时间均会变长。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏的特征</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>有8位富有个性的角色们<br></li><li>积极的攻击即是通往胜利的秘诀！流畅的游戏系统<br></li><li>十分气派的必杀技演出<br></li><li>可与电脑玩家对战的故事模式<br></li><li>可与喜欢的角色对战的VS模式<br></li><li>可以尽情磨练自己技巧的练习模式</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >*如欲游玩本游戏必须安装DirectPlay。</h2>您使用的PC如果尚未安装DirectPlay时，初次启动游戏时会安装DirectPlay。<br><br>若DirectPlay安装时取消或是没有正常安装时，按照以下的步骤重新安装。：<br>1.按下键盘的Windows键+R。<br>2.在字段内输入&quot;appwiz.cpl&quot;后按Enter。<br>3.按下「开启或关闭Windows 功能」。<br>4.勾选Legacy Components＞DirectPlay",
